text: Miha Šimenc (born 21 December 1995) is a Slovenian cross-country skier. He competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Slovenian male cross-country skiers Category:Tour de Ski skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Slovenia
